column2: "Hee hee! Nice work! I don't even have to read your report to see that. You really had some fine moves!"
"You sure made those hostiles dance and suffer before you wiped them out completely. Your Ranger skills are just dreamy."
"That felt great. Really satisfying. I just know I was built for times like these."
"I know my tastes are kind of special, but what's a girl to do? I like what I like."
"Next time, let's make even more hostiles suffer and suffer and then suffer some more!"
